n-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <div><div><div><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/A41802_p20023-1.png\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE A/418/02 Pizza Stone For Maxi Oven</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>182.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+am476\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/AM476_p20029.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE AM4-76 30 inch Stainless Steel Backsplash</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>265.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+ea2633006000008\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/EA2633006000008_p16230-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE EA2633006000008 Stainless Steel Wire Grid Grates For Stacking on Maxi Oven Drip Tray</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>84.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+ea4053004030006\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/EA4053004030006_p16234-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE EA4053004030006 Drip Pan For Maxi Oven</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>140.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Antique White\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Brass\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 30 inch Majestic II Induction Range (Antique White / Copper / Triple Glass Door) - UMI30NE3AWP\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI30NE3AWP\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780-3.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_168222-4.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_168223-4.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_168224-4.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_10608-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_168236-4.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_10609-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_10610-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3AWP_p12780_10611-3.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"7990.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202194020\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The Majestic 30 induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has four efficient element zones, a total oven capacity of four cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Order now for delivery in 90 to 120 days!</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that exudes elegance and functionality in equal measure. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies. Despite its ability to blend into any setting, Majestic commands attention.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of remaining heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Ensuring the safety of children</li><li>A full-touch display measuring 4.3 inches</li><li>Fire safety and prevention of overheating</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Getting started with little</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Technology for Products</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, guaranteeing the best satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Gas Range (Oven) Technology</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>Using cutting-edge technology in a stylish and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) expedite the cooking process while minimizing the risk of burns and other food hazards. Induction also helps with cleaning, energy savings, safety, temperature control, and cooking speed, all of which are important when it comes to preparing meals and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Determinant of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Automatically Stops the Timer</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Limiting Heat and Preventing Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>A safety feature will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Impressive Size and Power: The Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 30-inch range offers a maximum oven capacity of 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven to accommodate even the largest of dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Controlling Temperature with Electronic Precision</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>Displaying every function with clear and immediate graphics, the display guarantees superior readability thanks to TFT technology.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>With a single touch of the big screen, you can control all the features of either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously. You can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the ovens to start and stop cooking automatically.</p><p></p><p><strong>Doors with a Gentle Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Tester</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Hot Food Preparation)</strong></p><p>For a crispy baked dish or a juicy roast, this system draws out the vapours from within the cavity, giving you the option to cook it dry or wet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>You can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes in an ILVE oven, whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or using low heat.</p><p></p><p><strong>Using High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Effortless Cleaning with the Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</p><p></p><p><strong>Functions of the Oven. UOV 76 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing from Freeze</li><li>Prolonged cooking time</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>Cooking with a fan grill</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>An Underground Kitchen</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Constant, everyday cooking</li><li>Damp static regular cooking</li><li>Using a number of fans to cook</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>This oven is perfect for baking pizza, bread, focaccia, and other similar foods. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and it works in tandem with the other, less powerful heating elements to provide the ideal conditions for baking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>It guarantees that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>This steam-discharge cooker guarantees rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for foods that require a crunchy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, fish with a salt crust, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accelerated Launch</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extremely Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enclosure for Grilling</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Delicately Cooked Food from Above</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>Pastries (such as biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, and so on) are best cooked in this way to finish the cooking cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>Standard static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Fans</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Moist Fans</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Eco-Friendly Recipients</strong></p><p>Slow roasting foods, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, and delicate pastries, necessitate longer cooking times when using the ECO function, which significantly reduces power consumption. However, this cooking cycle is not meant for foods that are frozen.</p><p></p><p><strong>Proposition 65 in California\\u2014</strong></p><p>Caution: Potential Cancer and Reproductive Risks</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov for more regulations in your state.</a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\