" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE A/418/02 Pizza Stone For Maxi Oven</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>182.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+am476\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/AM476_p20029.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE AM4-76 30 inch Stainless Steel Backsplash</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>265.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+ea2633006000008\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/EA2633006000008_p16230-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE EA2633006000008 Stainless Steel Wire Grid Grates For Stacking on Maxi Oven Drip Tray</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>84.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+ea4053004030006\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/EA4053004030006_p16234-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE EA4053004030006 Drip Pan For Maxi Oven</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>140.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Burgundy\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Brass\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 30 inch Majestic II Induction Range (Burgundy / Copper / Triple Glass Door) - UMI30NE3BUP\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI30NE3BUP\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796-2.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_168272-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_168273-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_168274-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_10656-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_168593-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_10657-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_10658-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3BUP_p12796_10659-2.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"7990.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202194044\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The Majestic 30 induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has four efficient element zones, a total oven capacity of four cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Availability: 90 - 120 days for pre-order</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that exudes elegance and functionality in equal measure. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies. Despite its ability to blend into any setting, Majestic commands attention.</p><p></p><p>With their ornate details and rounded forms crafted from pure steel, majestic range cookers are kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative pieces.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of remaining heat</li><li>Timer with built-in self-exclusion</li><li>Bridge management</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Handles for sliding</li><li>Ensuring children's safety</li><li>Widescreen 4.3-inch</li><li>Preventing overheating and liquid spillage</li><li>Accurate electronic temperature regulation</li><li>A brief introduction</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Technology for Products</strong></p><p></p><p>Although aesthetics are important, having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE offers solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, combining these factors to guarantee the best satisfaction.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Electric Range (Stove)</strong></p><p>With their modern technology and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) make cooking a breeze. Induction offers many benefits, such as safe cooking, reduced energy consumption, safety, adjustable temperature control, and quick cooking times, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>At the end of the specified time, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Facilitates rapid boiling and cooking by directing the full power of the induction cooktop's (hob's) electromagnetic field to a predetermined area.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Keeping Things From Overheating and Leaking Liquids</strong></p><p>A safety feature will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>In our 30-inch range, you'll find a single or double combination oven with a capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you'll have more than enough room to bake even the largest of dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>4.3\\\" Touch Screen Display</strong></p><p>Displaying every function with clear and immediate graphics, the display guarantees superior readability thanks to TFT technology.</p><p></p><p><strong>The TFT display is user-friendly, comprehensive, and has a high resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Door with a System for Soft Closing</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Cooking Probe</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Extraction for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>With this system, the vapours are drawn out from within the cavity, giving you the option for a more or less moist cooking, so you can get a crunchy baked dish or a juicy roast.</p><p></p><p><strong>Range of temperatures: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit.</strong></p><p>Whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or cooking at a low temperature, an ILVE oven can make even the most difficult recipes taste delicious.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Shields kitchen and oven-related furniture from dangerously high temperatures.</p><p></p><p><strong>Effortless Cleaning with the Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Domestic Operations. UOV 76 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>A brief introduction</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Cooking with a fan grill</li><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>Starting with the base</li><li>Preparing moist food from below</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Normal static cooking that is moist</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking options</li><li>Several wet fan ovens</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>Ensures that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>The steam discharge ensures rapid and intense cooking, making it ideal for foods that require a crunchy texture, such as baked potatoes and vegetables, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rapid Start</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Cooked with Moisture</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enclosure for Grilling</strong></p><p>This grilling function is ideal for browning and roasting meat, fish, vegetables, fillets, Florentine steak, and other types of meat quickly and thoroughly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Cooking</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, and many more foods benefit from this function's browning and color-enhancing capabilities.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Preparing Food from the Ground Up</strong></p><p>Pastries (such as biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, and so on) are best cooked in this way to finish the cooking cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>This makes traditional static cooking even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>This makes regular cooking with multiple fans even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Sustainable Cuisine</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measure 65 in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Potential Cancer and Reproductive Risks</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">For more information, visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.</a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">Sorry, but the video tag isn't compatible with your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div