rid Grates For Stacking on Maxi Oven Drip Tray</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>84.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+ea4053004030006\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/EA4053004030006_p16234-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE EA4053004030006 Drip Pan For Maxi Oven</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>140.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Stainless Steel\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Burnished\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 30 inch Majestic II Induction Range (Stainless Steel / Chrome / Triple Glass Door) - UMI30NE3SSC\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI30NE3SSC\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834-2.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_168447-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_168448-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_168449-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_15485-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_168919-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_10745-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_10746-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_10747-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30NE3SSC_p12834_15486-2.webp\"], \"Variant Price\": \"7990.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202188678\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>Featuring a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, four precise and efficient element zones, and a total oven capacity of four cubic feet, the Majestic 30-inch induction range combines traditional Italian design with state-of-the-art technology.</p><p>Product Status: Available</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>A freestanding showpiece with a style characterized by rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technology originating from the realm of professional cooking, Majestic is a marriage of form and function, the perfect range cooker. Its beauty and functionality are expertly embodied.</p><p></p><p>Majestic range cookers are works of art in and of themselves, but they also serve as functional kitchen appliances because of the meticulous craftsmanship that goes into their curved, all-steel designs.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>The indicator for residual heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Manage bridges</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Ensuring the safety of children</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Prevention of overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Getting started quickly</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, guaranteeing the best satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Electric Range (Head)</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Timer with Built-In Stop Function</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>This feature allows you to control two adjacent zones on induction cooktops (hobs) with one command, as if they were one large zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Facilitates rapid boiling and cooking by directing the full power of the induction cooktop's (hob's) electromagnetic field to a predetermined area.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protecting Children</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Prevention of Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Massive and Efficient Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 30-inch range offers a maximum oven capacity of 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven to accommodate even the largest of dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>Unlike with traditional ovens, the temperature of the oven will stay consistent thanks to the electronic control.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>The screen guarantees excellent legibility with TFT technology, showing every function with clear and immediate graphics.</p><p></p><p><strong>The TFT display is user-friendly, comprehensive, and has a high resolution.</strong></p><p>With a single touch of the big screen, you can control all the features of either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously. You can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the ovens to start and stop cooking automatically.</p><p></p><p><strong>Door with a System for Soft Closing</strong></p><p>Shock absorbers installed in the door hinges allow for quieter, more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Tester</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Soggie Cooking)</strong></p><p>If you want a crispy baked dish or a juicy roast, this system will remove the vapours from inside the cavity, giving you the option to cook it dry or wet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Using High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Shields kitchen and oven-related furniture from dangerously high temperatures.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Convenient Way to Clean Your Grill Every Time</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking in the Oven: UOV 76 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing from Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>Cooking with a fan grill</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>An Underground Kitchen</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Cooking that is moist and static</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>Perfect for baking pizza, bread, and focaccia. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and with the assistance of the other, less powerful heating elements, it produces the ideal conditions for this kind of cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>It guarantees that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accelerated Boot</strong></p><p>Rapid preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>The steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking, making it ideal for moist foods like salt cod, stewed rabbit, braised meat, chicken cacciatore, and braised meats.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enclosure for Grilling</strong></p><p>Use this function for browning and roasting meat, fish, vegetables, fillets, Florentine steak, and other types of meat quickly and thoroughly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>This function is perfect for browning and finishing a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. all benefit from it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Delicately Cooked Food from Above</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>For pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking the cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Standard, Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Wet Static Regular Cooking</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Low-Cost Ethical Cuisine</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Proposition 65 in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Potential Risks to Health and Fertility</p><p><strong><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov for more information.</a></strong></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">Sorry, but the video tag isn't compatible with your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/re1Uo4qdmcc.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\"