ve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Antique White\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Chrome\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Solid Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 30 inch Majestic II Induction Range (Antique White / Brass / Solid Door) - UMI30QNE3AWG\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI30QNE3AWG\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775-2.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_168579-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_168580-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_168581-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_169155-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_169156-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_10765-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_10766-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3AWG_p12775_10767-2.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"8690.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202223553\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>With a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, four precise and efficient element zones, and a total oven capacity of four cubic feet, the Majestic 30-inch induction range combines traditional Italian design with state-of-the-art technology.</p><p>Order now for delivery in 90 to 120 days!</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic, a freestanding statement-piece with a style that incorporates rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technologies derived from the world of professional cooking, is a beautiful and functional fusion of form and function. It effortlessly blends into any setting while still taking center stage.</p><p></p><p>Majestic range cookers are works of art in and of themselves, but they also serve as functional kitchen appliances because of the meticulous craftsmanship that goes into their curved, all-steel designs.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Indictor for residual heat</li><li>Timer with built-in stop function</li><li>Bridge management</li><li>Booster role</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Keeping children safe</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Prevention of overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Fast start</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Innovations in Product Technologies</strong></p><p></p><p>When it comes to cooking, form follows function. ILVE puts its knowledge and expertise to work for you, providing solutions that combine high-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, ensuring the highest level of satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>Using cutting-edge technology in a stylish and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) expedite the cooking process while minimizing the risk of burns and other food hazards. Induction also helps with cleaning, energy savings, safety, temperature control, and cooking speed, all of which are important when it comes to preparing meals and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Detector of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>The glass is hot, so be careful not to touch it or put anything on it; doing so could cause damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Timer with Built-In Stop Function</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Bridge Management</strong></p><p>This feature allows you to control two adjacent zones on induction cooktops (hobs) with one command, as if they were one large zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>You can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob) once this feature is enabled; it remains disabled until you disable it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Preventing Liquid Spills and Overheating</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Massive and Efficient Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 30-inch range offers a maximum oven capacity of 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven to accommodate even the largest of dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Electronic Temperature Control with High Precision</strong><