LVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Glossy Black\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Chrome\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Solid Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 30 inch Majestic II Induction Range (Glossy Black / Brass / Solid Door) - UMI30QNE3BKG\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMI30QNE3BKG\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815-2.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_168616-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_168617-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_168618-3.webp\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_169196-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_169197-3.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_10797-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_10798-2.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMI30QNE3BKG_p12815_10799-2.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"8690.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202223591\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>Featuring a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, four precise and efficient element zones, and a total oven capacity of four cubic feet, the Majestic 30-inch induction range combines traditional Italian design with state-of-the-art technology.</p><p>Product Status: Available</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>The show-stopping range cooker that will turn your kitchen into a showpiece.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that exudes elegance and functionality in equal measure. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies. Despite its ability to blend into any setting, Majestic commands attention.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>Designed for your home's kitchen, these workhorses are available in a variety of colors (from 30 to 60 inches) and set-up options (from multiple options) and can be customized to RAL Classic shades upon request. They also feature fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of residual heat</li><li>Timer with built-in self-exclusion</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Protecting children</li><li>Full touch display measuring 4.3 inches</li><li>Fire safety and prevention of overheating</li><li>Electronic temperature control with pinpoint accuracy</li><li>Getting started with little</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Technology for Products</strong></p><p></p><p>Although aesthetics are important, having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE offers solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, combining these factors to guarantee the best satisfaction.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Heat Residue Indicator</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Bridge Management</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Facilitates rapid boiling and cooking by directing the full power of the induction cooktop's (hob's) electromagnetic field to a predetermined area.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Keeping Things From Overheating and Leaking Liquids</strong></p><p>A safety feature will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>Our 30-inch range offers a maximum oven capacity of 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven to accommodate even the largest of dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>Unlike with traditional ovens, the temperature of the oven will stay consistent thanks to the electronic control.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>The display guarantees excellent readability with TFT technology, showing every function with clear and immediate graphics.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Comfortably Closing Door System</strong></p><p>With the shock absorber installed in the door hinges, closing the door is a more gradual and noiseless process.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Cooking Probe</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Soggie Cooking)</strong></p><p>With this system, the vapours are drawn out from within the cavity, giving you the option for a more or less moist cooking, so you can get a crunchy baked dish or a juicy roast.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Ultimate Cleaning Solution: A Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>The electric heating element of the grill can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, thanks to the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking in the Oven: UOV 76 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>A brief overview</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Cooking with a fan grill</li><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Recipes viewed from above</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Cooking that is moist and static</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking options</li><li>Several wet fan ovens</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>Ensures that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking to the Extremes</strong></p><p>The steam discharge ensures rapid and intense cooking, making it ideal for foods that require a crunchy texture, such as baked potatoes and vegetables, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Easy Beginning</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking on a Grill with a Closed Door</strong></p><p>Ideal for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and even veggies quickly and 